Library for easy usage of observable pattern.

>>> @interface
>>> class SampleListener(Listen):
>>>     @event
>>>     def foo(self,a,b,c):
>>>         raise NotImplementedError
>>> 
>>> class Sample(SampleListener):
>>>     def foo(self,a,b,c):
>>>         print a,b,c
>>> 
>>> a = Sample()
>>> SampleListener.foo(1,2,c=3)
1 2 3
